  "description" : "[h1]Project FR: Stardust & MetaGUI - High-End Interface Localization[/h1]\n\n[b]Project FR: Stardust Module[/b] is an essential technical extension for the Core Engine. This module doesn't just translate text; it bypasses the structural limitations of Stardust Core Lite to ensure your quickbar, menus, and themes stay fully in French, even when the mod tries to force English defaults.\n\n[h2]✨ Features:[/h2]\n[list]\n[] [b]Full MetaGUI Support:[/b] Every settings menu, apply/cancel button, and tab within the MetaGUI framework is localized.\n[] [b]Dynamic Quickbar Translation:[/b] Icons and tooltips in the Quickbar (Matter Manipulator, Navigation, Codex, etc.) are translated on-the-fly using technical IDs.\n[] [b]Curated Themes:[/b] Elegant French descriptions for Stardust themes (Carbon, Chroma, Starbound Classic) to match the original aesthetic.\n[] [b]Priority Override:[/b] Uses targeted Lua script modifications to stay active even when Stardust uses \"replaced: true\" on vanilla interfaces.\n[/list]\n\n[h2]🛠️ Why is this module required?[/h2]\nStardust Core Lite is a powerful overhaul that replaces many vanilla files, often breaking standard translation patches. [b]Project FR: Stardust[/b] acts as a high-priority bridge, re-injecting the French localization directly into the Stardust scripts for a seamless experience.\n\n[h2]📥 Requirements:[/h2]\nThis module is part of the Project FR ecosystem and requires:\n[list]\n[] [b]Project FR: Core Engine[/b] (The heart of the translation).\n[] [b]Stardust Core Lite[/b] (The original mod by Stardust).\n[/list]\n\n[h2]🚧 Status (v1.0):[/h2]\n[list]\n[] [b]Settings & General UI:[/b] 100%\n[] [b]Quickbar Icons & Tooltips:[/b] 100%\n[] [b]Theme Names & Descriptions:[/b] 100%\n[] [b]MM Upgrade Window:[/b] Fully integrated and translated.\n[/list]\n\n[hr][/hr]\n\n[h3]📜 Credits & Acknowledgments:[/h3]\n[b]Project FR: Stardust[/b] is a localized enhancement of the original Stardust Core Lite mod.\n[list]\n[] [b]Technical Adaptation:[/b] Specific Lua scripts from Stardust/MetaGUI were modified by [i]Neshkel[/i] to integrate the Project FR dynamic translation engine.\n[] [b]Interface Patching:[/b] The Matter Manipulator (MM) and various UI elements are localized via targeted JSON patches for maximum compatibility.\n[*] [b]Framework:[/b] Original logic, UI design, and MetaGUI framework are the work of [b]Stardust[/b].\n[/list]\n\n[b]License:[/b] Released under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.",
